OL,7,FThe Scottish whisky industry has
OL,8,Fcondemned Jeremy Hunt's decision to
OL,9,Fraise tax on the drink by 10.1 per cent
OL,10,Fin his Budget, in what it said was one
OL,11,Fof the biggest rises in duty for
OL,12,Fdecades.
OL,14,FThe Scotch Whisky Association (SWA)
OL,15,Fsaid the move would "further increase
OL,16,Fthe competitive disadvantage faced by
OL,17,Fspirits" and meant that 75 per cent of
OL,18,Fthe price of the average bottle would
OL,19,Fnow go to HMRC.
